Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer for sale on behalf 36 Laver Drive, Robina - Gold Coast, a superb free standing office building strategically located in the master planned Robina Town Centre precinct on the Gold Coast.

With a gateway position on a 2,495sqm* site in the Robina Town Centre precinct, 36 Laver Drive benefits from direct access to one of the state's fastest growing residential and commercial regions. Robina is already recognised as one of the largest residential regions on the Gold Coast and is fast becoming the largest centralised office, retail and commercial hubs in the city.

Robina's strategic location and access to a local, educated and stable workforce has boosted its appeal as a commercial precinct and regional office location, and has attracted a range of high calibre government, national corporate and local businesses. Located nearby is Robina Town Centre - a 100,000sqm regional shopping centre with tenants such as David Jones, Coles, Woolworths, Target, Kmart, Myer and 220 specialty shops and service providers; Gold Coast Hospital (Robina Campus), Austar and many notable others.

Completed in mid 2006, 36 Laver Drive comprises a high quality 4 level office building consisting of two whole floors of offices and two levels of undercover car parking plus a reception and amenities area on the ground level. The gross area of the building is some 1,757sqm. There are additional external visitor car parks on site providing in total 94 car parking spaces on site representing a car parking ratio of 1:18sqm.

36 Laver Drive is now offered for sale vacant possession or for lease with immediate access available. Parties wishing to obtain further information or to arrange an inspection please contact the agents on the links above.

Modern Freestanding commercial office building completed 2006

89 Secure carparks over two levels with two street entries

Two full floor spaces can be split plus reception area on ground floor

HQ Branding opportunities to passing traffic

Lakehouse is focused on delivering an unrivalled working environment that supports creativity and collaboration from inside the office suites or via the breakout areas created in a lush landscaped ground level setting. The office buildings are nestled in a waterfront location accessed off Cheltenham Drive where upon entry through the stacked stone-wall driveway you will immediately sense the exclusive nature of what is on offer – the wide open spaces instill a relaxed and tranquil impression.

The Lakehouse strata suites are predominantly held by locally owned and operated businesses within industry sectors such as real estate, medical consulting, financial services and engineering who were drawn to the property because of its unrivalled offering including:

- Independence: each suite has independent controlled air conditioning, suites can be accessed 24/7, lift and stair access provides multi-mode movement around building
- Accessibility: centrally located between the Pacific Motorway & Bermuda Street tapping into an expansive north and southbound employee catchment and customer base
- Onsite Amenity: ample parking onsite plus free on-street parking, Lily Pond Café, landscaped breakout areas overlooking lake
- Local Community Engagement: walking distance to Miami Pavilion, popular restaurants such as Bunnath Kitchen & Spaghetti & Jazz, 7-Eleven service station, medical services, childcare services etc.


Only 1 suite remains for you to future proof your business in the new way of working that embraces independent tenancy control within a natural landscaped environment.

We encourage your interest in the final stages of this sales campaign by contacting Exclusive Sales Agent via links above.
